paragraphs: Popular American singer Billie Eilish will perform in Prague. The concert will take place on June 1, 2025 at the "O2 Arena". This was announced by the Prague-based concert organizing company LiveNation.
Ticket sales will start on Friday, May 3rd, at 10:00. You will be able to buy them on the Ticketportal website.
The ticket prices start from 1250 kroner.
The winner of two Oscars, two Golden Globes, and seven Grammys will perform in Prague as part of her world tour in support of her third album Hit Me Hard and Soft.
